		<title>小貓因天生畸形遭遺棄？好心志工救援幫助牠迎來新生！ </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/31/%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e5%9b%a0%e5%a4%a9%e7%94%9f%e7%95%b8%e5%bd%a2%e9%81%ad%e9%81%ba%e6%a3%84%ef%bc%9f%e5%a5%bd%e5%bf%83%e5%bf%97%e5%b7%a5%e6%95%91%e6%8f%b4%e5%b9%ab%e5%8a%a9%e7%89%a0%e8%bf%8e%e4%be%86/</link>
		
