		<title>貓狗飼料怎麼選？破解寵物糧食的這5大迷思不踩雷</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/30/%e8%b2%93%e7%8b%97%e9%a3%bc%e6%96%99%e6%80%8e%e9%ba%bc%e9%81%b8%ef%bc%9f%e7%a0%b4%e8%a7%a3%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e7%b3%a7%e9%a3%9f%e7%9a%84%e9%80%995%e5%a4%a7%e8%bf%b7%e6%80%9d%e4%b8%8d%e8%b8%a9%e9%9b%b7/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
